  stimulus_text = 'The novel follows a young woman, Maria, who is trying to find her place in the world.  She is struggling with the expectations that society places on her, and she is trying to figure out who she is and what she wants to do with her life.  Maria is also dealing with the challenges of being a woman in a patriarchal society, where she is often treated as less than equal to men.  She begins to question the traditional roles that society assigns to women, and she starts to find her own voice.  What is the central idea of the novel?',
